If you don't help them, no one will."],[5196,5305,"Where is she?"],[5305,5467,"The Soho Clubhouse."],[5467,5768,"Please help them or you will regret it."],[5976,6147,"Are you going to see Lottie?"],[6147,6352,"This is none of your concern."],[6352,6464,"How many times will you let her"],[6464,6573,"lead you around?"]],"49":[[45,346,"Lottie, I'm so glad you came."],[346,529,"You didn't give me much of a choice."],[529,629,"Where's my daughter?"],[629,825,"Relax! She's fine."],[825,1017,"Come, have a drink."],[1017,1121,"Let's catch up."],[1121,1209,"No!"],[1209,1388,"I want nothing to do with you."],[1618,1785,"You're all monsters!"],[1835,1947,"Ooh!"],[1947,2177,"Crash and burn, Lance."],[2289,2531,"No one says ‘NO’ to me."],[2823,2882,"No."],[3007,3086,"No!"],[3132,3328,"Campus belle Lottie,"],[3328,3436,"you're more gorgeous than"],[3436,3545,"in college."],[3545,3661,"You remember us?"],[3716,3916,"Or we remember you. That body."],[4054,4137,"I’ve been wanting to taste again"],[4137,4208,"ever since."],[4208,4341,"Get in line, boys."],[4341,4479,"Oh my God."],[4629,4838,"Stop pretending you don't like it, bitch."],[4838,4884,"No!"],[4884,5017,"Don't touch me!"],[5709,5847,"Let her go."],[5910,6118,"Jack! He came for me!"],[6135,6260,"What the fuck?"],[6260,6452,"Jack Kline actually showed up!"],[6452,6531,"Lottie must have a"],[6531,6664,"magic bag or something."],[6664,6752,"Why doesn't he just"],[6752,6865,"cut her loose already?"],[6940,7140,"Lottie, we're leaving."],[7273,7486,"In case you didn't get it yet, Jack."],[7532,7732,"Lottie is my girl now."],[7857,8124,"Don't forget, I got your daughter."],[8124,8254,"She kept crying,"],[8254,8425,"screaming for her mommy."],[8516,8583,"Bailey."],[8583,8725,"I’m here, Bailey."],[8904,9013,"Lottie, come."],[9071,9296,"Sit on my lap. Now!"]],"50":[[0,300,"I'm sorry, Jack. But my baby needs me."],[375,554,"She's so sick."],[554,855,"And now she's alone and scared."],[1222,1522,"Lottie, don't do this."],[2031,2331,"Lottie is Lance's girl."],[2535,2631,"But she's also"],[2631,2836,"Brandon's and Josh's."],[2848,3040,"She slept with all of them in college."],[3040,3157,"Stop! Stop!"],[3157,3211,"No."],[3257,3428,"Lottie Alcott,"],[3470,3611,"you’re shameless."],[3611,3695,"What can you expect"],[3695,3862,"from a gold digger?"],[3899,3987,"Here Lottie,"],[4012,4170,"give Jack a drink."],[4170,4412,"He looks like he needs one."],[5355,5701,"Lottie, what they’re saying is true?"],[5943,6110,"Yes."],[6835,7073,"Lottie, you are a whore."]],"51":[[250,446,"What's this?"],[742,1038,"What is this?"],[1305,1451,"Why do you still have this?"],[1451,1497,"Jack, please,"],[1497,1701,"it's mine."],[1960,2131,"I gave you this"],[2131,2373,"to promise that I'd marry you one day."],[2540,2840,"And you broke that promise."],[2857,3157,"That ring is so pretty."],[3215,3349,"I like it."],[3445,3520,"You like it?"],[3920,4079,"Then you can have it."],[4079,4216,"Jack! No, please. Please!"],[4216,4341,"I’m begging-"],[4683,5034,"My last memory of us gone."],[5226,5380,"Madison,"],[5518,5701,"would you marry me this weekend?"],[5922,5997,"Yes!"],[5997,6106,"Kiss! Kiss!"],[6114,6235,"Kiss! Kiss!"],[6243,6377,"Kiss! Kiss!"],[6377,6602,"Kiss! Kiss! Kiss! Kiss!"]],"52":[[342,421,"Looks like Jack's"],[421,604,"finally done with you, Lottie."],[646,942,"What a pathetic loser."],[1488,1722,"Mommy!"],[1722,2022,"Oh, my baby! My baby!"],[2339,2427,"Mommy, don’t cry."],[2427,2531,"It's okay. Bailey’s here."],[2531,2711,"I'll protect you."],[3182,3286,"Mommy, where are"],[3286,3428,"Grandma and Uncle Mikey?"],[3474,3636,"They sold their daughter."],[3636,3737,"Why live in a dump"],[3737,3937,"when they have all that money?"],[3983,4195,"It's just you and me now, okay?"],[4195,4275,"Why don't you rest"],[4275,4496,"and I'll clean this up?"],[5484,5626,"My phone!"],[5626,5722,"I haven't seen it"],[5722,5818,"since my mom took it from me"],[5818,5943,"at the mental hospital."],[6022,6231,"Jack said he called me."],[6452,6631,"Oh my God."],[6631,6998,"1608 missed calls from Jack."],[7290,7424,"Lottie."]],"53":[[33,316,"Lottie, I'm at a hospital in the UK."],[525,763,"I just had brain surgery."],[763,1063,"My head really hurts right now."],[1084,1330,"I really need to see you."],[1330,1393,"If you come,"],[1393,1551,"I can pretend nothing happened."],[1914,2164,"Today my law firm went public."],[2164,2302,"I'm rich now."],[2302,2515,"Lottie, you wanted a rich husband."],[2515,2727,"I finally become your dream guy."],[2727,3028,"So please answer the phone."],[3211,3424,"Lottie, just admit you were wrong."],[3424,3520,"We can make up and"],[3520,3724,"start over, together."],[4312,4554,"Lottie, it's been nine years."],[4600,4688,"I'm about to become"],[4688,4896,"engaged to Madison."],[4925,5226,"But I still feel this need to call you."],[5413,5714,"Lottie, you broke my heart."],[6118,6393,"I can't believe I'm still calling you."],[6393,6606,"I never lost a case."],[6606,6923,"They call me Mr. Untouchable."],[6977,7144,"But they're wrong."],[7144,7365,"I lost the most important thing"],[7365,7478,"in my life."],[7574,7695,"You."],[7811,7870,"Mommy, look!"],[7870,8170,"It’s Jack!"],[8491,8758,"Mommy, if you want Jack, just go."],[8796,8996,"It's not that simple, Bailey."],[8996,9288,"He already called you 1608 times."],[9288,9467,"It's your turn."]],"54":[[1405,1526,"What do you want?"],[1526,1676,"Last time Jack showed up"],[1676,1797,"to save you."],[1797,1939,"You were lucky."],[1939,2110,"But now he's getting married."],[2110,2410,"Let's see who tries to save you now."],[2744,2861,"The crime you committed,"],[2861,3086,"I still have the evidence!"],[3086,3253,"Leave or I'll press charges!"],[3528,3870,"This just proves that you got burned"],[3870,4058,"and that you’re deaf,"],[4058,4225,"proves that you're a tramp."],[4362,4483,"What do you guys think?"],[4483,4654,"It can't prove that we hurt her, right?"],[4808,4992,"I really want to get laid."],[5050,5167,"No! No!"],[5572,5809,"No one saved you back then,"],[5809,6110,"no one is going to save you now."],[6177,6427,"Stop struggling, Lottie."],[6427,6581,"It's useless."],[6581,6706,"No!"],[7540,7603,"And do you,"],[7603,7845,"Jack Kline, take Madison Foster"],[7845,8053,"to be your lawfully wedded wife?"],[8166,8329,"He doesn't want to."],[8512,8604,"Bailey?"],[8604,8712,"That's Lottie's kid."],[8712,8846,"What's she doing here?"],[8883,8975,"We're in the middle of the wedding!"],[8975,9075,"This isn't the time, nor"],[9075,9238,"the place for nonsense."],[9238,9367,"Get rid of her."],[9367,9505,"Wait, wait!"],[9505,9672,"Someone's bullying my mommy!"],[9672,9718,"Years ago,"],[9718,9868,"they locked her in a darkroom,"],[9868,10055,"used a curling iron to burn her body."],[10055,10285,"They hurt her right hand and her ear."],[10381,10489,"They even raped my mommy."],[10489,10785,"That's why I was born."],[10960,11052,"What did you just say?"]],"55":[[325,454,"Is this true?"],[533,679,"After you left, my mommy"],[679,784,"got really sick."],[784,930,"They put her in a mental hospital."],[930,1096,"She missed you every day."],[1096,1222,"When we watched TV,"],[1222,1434,"when she saw your face, she'd smile."],[1434,1659,"But her face was always wet."],[1659,1760,"My mommy never stopped"],[1760,1897,"loving you."],[1935,2077,"Jack, they're back at our house."],[2077,2214,"They're hurting her again."],[2214,2414,"Please save my mommy."],[3244,3482,"Stop struggling, Lottie."],[3482,3591,"I’ll give you 3 million"],[3591,3716,"if I fuck you this time."],[4491,4792,"Get off her now!"],[5067,5171,"She cried out for you"],[5171,5309,"when I fucked her."],[5309,5476,"But you didn't come."],[5705,5809,"Jack! Jack!"],[5809,6110,"You’ll kill him!"],[7032,7332,"No. No, this can't be real."],[7540,7745,"I didn't know about this. I-"],[7745,7878,"How come I didn't know anything?"]],"56":[[33,233,"I was going to tell you"],[233,342,"that night at the hospital"],[342,429,"when my dad died."],[429,617,"But you, your grandpa,"],[617,900,"he told me about your surgery."],[980,1188,"He said I had to let you go."],[1351,1488,"My life,"],[1509,1605,"fell apart after that."],[1605,1889,"I didn't want to drag you down with me."],[1956,2193,"I'm sorry that you have to see this."],[2506,2623,"You pushed me away"],[2623,2806,"nine years ago."],[2952,3169,"I won’t ever let you do that again."],[3257,3461,"Jack, I wasn’t ignoring your calls."],[3461,3695,"I was sick, I was depressed."],[3724,3887,"I know."],[3887,4208,"I blamed you I, I hated you, I-"],[4354,4429,"because I thought"],[4429,4629,"you wouldn't want me."],[4771,5009,"And all this time,"],[5009,5221,"you thought I wouldn't want you."],[5872,6172,"Marry me."],[6873,7119,"Lottie Alcott,"],[7119,7340,"would you do me the honor"],[7340,7494,"of becoming my wife?"],[9184,9480,"Bailey, your mommy and I"],[9480,9780,"are getting married."],[9813,9964,"You're going to be our daughter."],[9964,10197,"I'm going to adopt you, sweetheart."],[10197,10477,"I’d like that, Jack."],[10477,10602,"But I have leukemia."],[10602,10902,"I'm dying."],[11207,11524,"No. I'm going to get"],[11524,11824,"you the best doctors in the world."],[11866,12012,"Jack."],[12012,12166,"She's our daughter."],[12166,12249,"And if she's anything"],[12249,12466,"like her mother, she'll pull through."],[12529,12679,"I promise you."],[12679,12829,"We're a team now, Lottie."],[12871,12987,"And I will protect you with"],[12987,13171,"everything I got."],[13267,13492,"And those bastards who hurt you,"],[13492,13705,"we're taking them down."],[13705,14018,"Justice may be late, but it's coming."]],"57":[[12,133,"Mr. Kline! Mr. Kline!"],[141,316,"We heard your latest cases about"],[316,571,"campus bullying, gang rape,"],[583,742,"leading to a disability."],[742,875,"Who's the plaintiff?"],[942,1151,"I am."],[1180,1405,"My name is Lottie Alcott."],[1455,1651,"Most women who are attacked"],[1651,1926,"are afraid to speak out."],[1926,2173,"For nine years,"],[2173,2385,"I cried, begged,"],[2385,2615,"and believed that I was wrong."],[2706,3007,"But now I know it's not my fault."],[3082,3299,"Lottie Alcott is my wife."],[3370,3570,"And I'm fighting for her."],[4154,4408,"And I'm fighting for her."],[4408,4571,"No further questions."],[4758,5017,"Nice speech."],[5017,5313,"Prepared for your first loss though."],[5372,5643,"What does Lottie have that I don't?"],[5643,5839,"Why does Jack love her and not me?"],[5872,6043,"You and I are the same."],[6085,6264,"I was jealous like you."],[6264,6381,"Nine years ago,"],[6381,6606,"Lottie stole Jack from me."],[6606,6798,"I want Lottie dead."],[6798,7023,"Trial is tomorrow."],[7023,7144,"You guys will definitely win."],[7144,7332,"He shouldn't have taken the case."],[7332,7540,"It's a classic ‘he said, she said’."],[7540,7741,"Lottie will be ruined,"],[7741,7841,"Jack with her."],[7978,8158,"I want to watch her suffer."],[8779,9075,"Then you're going to love this."],[9292,9367,"Come one Lottie."],[9367,9613,"Give us a smile."]],"58":[[513,813,"This court is officially in session."],[846,1001,"Nine years ago,"],[1001,1163,"Lottie Alcott let us"],[1163,1334,"play with her willingly."],[1380,1543,"We even have witnesses"],[1543,1639,"to back us up."],[2702,2894,"Her own family will testify"],[2894,3107,"she did it for money."],[3107,3278,"I have a copy of the check."],[3349,3699,"Lottie was paid half a million dollars."],[3749,4004,"Your wife is just a gold digger"],[4004,4104,"and a whore."],[4300,4441,"Your good reputation"],[4441,4554,"is going to be destroyed"],[4554,4667,"being with her."],[4746,4942,"It's too bad you let her be with you"],[4942,5080,"and took this case."],[5196,5342,"Would you like to cross-examine"],[5342,5484,"this witness, Mr. Kline?"],[5509,5663,"No, your honor."],[6185,6331,"The defense has a witness."],[6331,6485,"We'd like to call to the stand."],[6506,6723,"What fucking witness?"]],"59":[[633,754,"Where were you last night,"],[754,888,"Miss Foster?"],[988,1080,"I was having drinks"],[1080,1255,"with Taylor and her friends."],[1292,1401,"That's when Taylor admitted that"],[1401,1522,"nine years ago,"],[1522,1730,"she and her friends bullied Lottie Alcott"],[1730,1835,"and brutally raped her."],[1939,2056,"Fucking lie!"],[2139,2318,"There will be order."],[2318,2439,"Sit down."],[2439,2602,"You are out of order."],[2694,2944,"I have evidence."],[3586,3812,"Come on, Lottie. Give us a smile."],[3978,4237,"Oh!"],[4404,4504,"Turn it off!"],[4546,4738,"Turn it off!"],[4738,4921,"You conniving,"],[4921,5221,"backstabbing bitch!"],[5255,5367,"That is out of order."],[5367,5509,"Sit down, ma'am."],[5509,5722,"Sit down or you'll be held in contempt."],[5755,5964,"I'm not like you."],[5964,6068,"When you showed me that video"],[6068,6218,"last night, I threw up."],[6302,6602,"We are human beings, not animals."],[6702,7002,"Women should help other women."],[7344,7645,"The order of this court is as follows."],[7749,7932,"You have all been found guilty"],[7932,8279,"of bullying and rape,"],[8387,8500,"and are sentenced"],[8500,8779,"to 25 years in prison."],[9284,9392,"Order in the court."],[9392,9588,"There will be order."],[9588,9826,"I've also issued a warrant"],[9826,9980,"for the arrest"],[9980,10331,"of Bobbi and Mikey Alcott"],[10331,10635,"for bribery and perjury."],[10660,10760,"Lottie, help us!"],[10760,10915,"Sis, no!"],[10944,11098,"Take them into custody, Deputy."],[11102,11269,"No, come on!"]],"60":[[421,617,"Hey, you okay?"],[650,867,"Yeah, I think I am."],[1309,1459,"Thank you,"],[1459,1622,"for what you did."],[1622,1931,"Lottile, we can never be friends."],[1985,2072,"But I wanted you to know"],[2072,2252,"that it's not your fault."],[2560,2686,"You're not alone."],[2686,2852,"It's not your fault."],[2932,3086,"Lottie, it's not your fault."],[3123,3311,"Lottie, it's not your fault."],[3403,3574,"It's not your fault."],[3978,4095,"Miss Lottie! Miss Lottie!"],[4129,4225,"What's your reaction to"],[4225,4362,"today's verdict?"],[4975,5142,"I want to tell the women"],[5142,5296,"who are suffering the same way"],[5296,5442,"that I did,"],[5530,5759,"if you've ever been hurt,"],[5759,5972,"don't be afraid."],[5972,6227,"Be brave."],[6227,6406,"Love will guide you to overcome"],[6406,6702,"the darkness."],[6823,6911,"One. Two."],[6911,7048,"Three."],[7048,7303,"I never thought the pain would fade,"],[7303,7432,"but it does."],[7432,7653,"I thought I would always live in fear."],[7653,7928,"But now live in hope."],[8124,8379,"Come play, Mommy!"],[8888,9034,"With love,"],[9034,9180,"all things are possible."]]}